{"tid":2253033,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金正恩駕臨中国人民志願軍浩園  為毛岸英墓送上蛋炒飯款式花籃","createTime":"2020-10-22T01:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T03:37:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f89d49d0174fcd98c7eb5e53d07ffffc192442fb","tid":2253033,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T01:42:31.000Z","msg":"北韓領袖金正恩參謁中國人民志願軍烈士陵園。<br />\n<br />\n朝中社報道，為紀念中國人民志願軍抗美援朝70週年，金正恩參謁了位於平安南道檜倉郡的中國人民志願軍烈士陵園，又向在戰爭中陣亡的毛澤東兒子毛岸英墓前獻花。<br />\n<br />\n金正恩表示，永遠不會遺忘中國人民志願軍的崇高靈魂及獻身精神，又說朝中兩國軍民獲得的勝利，在今天依然具有重大意義。報導說，金正恩昨日亦向位於平壤的朝中友誼塔獻上花籃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556054-20201022.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556054-20201022.htm&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPaGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=bdb92b44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556054-20201022.htm&h=2f620a52\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556054-20201022.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4b5f6654126e8768cde18c3060bd779344619940","tid":2253033,"uid":50502,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T01:43:52.000Z","msg":"金仔呢排pr 做得唔錯喎"},{"pid":"792d67b38344984d495a51037dbf0ab4246ccda3","tid":2253033,"uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T01:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DPdNkbLXcAAaJit.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDPdNkbLXcAAaJit.jpg&h=df9c86db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a0d0b35e0caa66f220f2a9bb03be2279c7bca32","tid":2253033,"uid":82068,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T01:47:11.000Z","msg":"收野啦病毒平<br />\n夠唔夠洗啊<br />\n係地獄有冇比鬼欺負你啊"},{"pid":"1e89e62aea086db28bdb89d4f672a255413ad4a8","tid":2253033,"uid":18012,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b5f6654126e8768cde18c3060bd779344619940